<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/faq.css">
  <title>FAQ</title>
  <style>
    .faq-toggle .fa-times {
      display: none;
    }

    .faq.active .fa-chevron-down {
      display: none;
    }

    .faq.active .fa-times {
      display: inline;
    }

    .red {
      color: red;
      margin: 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .faq {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .faq-title {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .faq-text {
      display: none;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .faq.active .faq-text {
      display: block;
    }

    .faq-toggle {
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  <div class="faq-container">
    <div class="faq active">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        What services does HomeHub Agency offer?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        At HomeHub Agency, we offer a comprehensive range of real estate services, including buying, selling, and renting properties. Our experienced professionals provide personalized support to ensure a smooth and stress-free transaction.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        How can HomeHub Agency help me sell my home?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        Our team uses market expertise and innovative strategies to secure the best possible price for your home. We handle all aspects of the selling process, from listing and marketing to negotiating offers and closing the deal.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>
    
    <div class="faq">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        What types of rental properties do you have available?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        We offer a diverse selection of rental properties to match various lifestyles and budgets. Whether you’re looking for an apartment, house, or condo, our agents will help you find the perfect rental home.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>
    
    <div class="faq">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        How do I start the process of buying a home with HomeHub Agency?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        Begin by scheduling an initial consultation with one of our knowledgeable agents. We’ll discuss your requirements and preferences, then guide you through the entire buying process, from property searches to finalizing the purchase.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>
    
    <div class="faq">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        What makes HomeHub Agency different from other real estate agencies?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        Our commitment to personalized service and exceptional support sets us apart. We go above and beyond to ensure every transaction is smooth and stress-free, making your home journey a positive experience.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>
    
    <div class="faq">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        Can you help with property management services?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        Yes, we offer property management services to help landlords manage their rental properties efficiently. Our services include tenant screening, rent collection, maintenance coordination, and more.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        How do you determine the value of a home for sale?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        We use a combination of market analysis, property condition assessment, and local real estate trends to accurately determine the value of a home. Our goal is to ensure you get the best possible price.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        Are there any additional fees for your services?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        We believe in transparency and will discuss any fees associated with our services upfront. Our aim is to provide exceptional value without any hidden costs.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        What should I expect during the initial consultation?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        During the initial consultation, we’ll discuss your real estate needs and goals. We’ll answer any questions you have and outline a customized plan to help you achieve your objectives, whether you’re buying, selling, or renting.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        How do I contact HomeHub Agency to get started?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        You can contact us via phone, email, or through our website. Our friendly team is ready to assist you and schedule an initial consultation to begin your home journey with HomeHub Agency.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/js/all.min.js"></script>
  <script>
    const toggles = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-toggle')

    toggles.forEach(toggle => {
      toggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
        toggle.parentNode.classList.toggle('active')
      })
    })
  </script>
</body>
</html>
